plot: Skip and his buxom lactating wife Muffy are a loving couple whose car gets stuck in Blade, Bertha and Snake's biker-gang land. After a parole officer takes advantage of Blade, her gang takes the innocence out of Skip and Muffy.
title: La Boomba
